msgid "What must be true in order to have В§0?\n"
"\n"
"On the one hand, if В§1 is true, then В§2 is true, because В§3 implies В§4, which implies В§5.\n"
"\n"
"Similar reasoning shows that if В§6 is true, then В§7 is true.\n"
"\n"
"Conversely, if *either* В§8 or В§9 are true, this does not necessarily imply that В§10 is true. Can you see why?\n"
"\n"
"However, if *both* В§11 and В§12 are true, then В§13 is true, as you can argue using the strategy of proof by cases.\n"
"\n"
