msgid "For the Boss Level of Equality World, you are asked to prove an equality of a more elaborate form than we've seen thus far.\n"
"\n"
"On the left-hand side of the equality is an element defined by\n"
"\n"
"* starting with a pair of elements В§0 and В§1,\n"
"* applying a function В§2 to the pair В§3, and\n"
"* then applying a function В§4 to the result.\n"
"\n"
"On the right-hand side of the equality is an element defined by\n"
"* starting with a pair of elements В§5 and В§6,\n"
"* applying a function В§7 to the pair В§8, and\n"
"* then applying a function В§9 to the result.\n"
"\n"
"In general, these elements would be distinct. However, we have assumed that we have equalities В§10, В§11, and В§12.\n"
