#: Game.Levels.ProductWorld.L01_Pairing
msgid "The introduction rule for product types tells us that elements of a product type В§0 are formed by *pairing* elements of type В§1 with elements of type В§2.\n"
"\n"
"Given an element В§3 and an element В§4 there is a corresponding element of the product type В§5 that is denoted by В§6.\n"
